                <msItem n="12" xml:id="b5">
                  <locus from="32b" to="33">Foll. 32b-33</locus>
                  <title ref="" type="supplied">That the words of Scripture and of the Fathers are spoken with moderation, as to sick persons, lest we should utterly perish from before the living God; but that we are not on this account to take them as an incitement to greater boldness in sin </title>
                  <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܥܠ ܗ̇ܝ ܕܡ̈ܠܐ ܕܟܬܒ̈ܐ ܐܝܟ ܕܠܘܬ ܟܪ̈ܝܗܐ̣. ܡܡܫܚܐܝܬ ܐܡܝܪ̈ܢ܆ ܕܕܠܡܐ ܢܐܒܕܘܢ ܓܡܝܪܐܝܬ ܡܢ ܐܠܗܐ ܚܝܐ. ܐܠܐ ܠܘ ܡܛܠܗܕܐ ܬܥܕܝܪܐ ܢܫܩܘܠ ܐܢܝܢ܇ ܠܦܪܗܣܝܐ ܝܬܝܪܬܐ ܕܠܘܬ ܚܛܝܬܐ.   
