                <msItem n="13" xml:id="b6">
                  <locus from="33b" to="34">Foll. 33b-34</locus>
                  <title ref="" type="supplied">How to preserve the beauties of the ascetic life, and how it becomes a means of glorifying God.</title>
                  <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܕܒܡܢܐ ܡܬܢܛܪܝܢ ܫܘܦܪ̈ܐ ܕܝܚܝܕܝܘܬܐ̣. ܘܕܐܝܟܢ ܬܗܘܐ ܥܠ̤ܬ ܬܫܒܘܚܬܗ ܕܐܠܗܐ   
